----------------
UH CAF Bug Tests
----------------

This directory contains a set of simple tests for bugs that were encountered
in the UH CAF implementation in the past. In this document, we list tests for
bugs which are still unresolved.

Current tests for unresolved bugs:

bug667_gasnet_vis_ampipe.caf
bug674_allocate_stmt.caf

These are Open64 unresolved bugs that we found, not specific to our
implementation:

bug669_pointer_cpnt_copy.caf
bug673_pointer_initialize.caf
